Print all sub arrays with sum is equal to zero

Given an array of integers, print all sub-arrays with 0 sum

Example:
input: { 3, 4, -7, 3, 1, 3, 1, -4, -2, -2 }

output:
The sub-arrays with 0 sum are:
{ 3, 4, -7 }
{ 4, -7, 3 }
{ -7, 3, 1, 3 }
{ 3, 1, -4 }
{ 3, 1, 3, 1, -4, -2, -2 }
{ 3, 4, -7, 3, 1, 3, 1, -4, -2, -2 }